Rip notes: Nothing Was Ripped

Mag Launcher and his team of explorers are contracted by the Archaeological Society to investigate the ruins
of the Northrop Continent in this RPG from Ubisoft/Sting.

In these huge multilevel dungeons lie treasures which Mag must recover and return to the mysterious society.
Choose 3 members of your squad to explore the dungeons and battle the monsters with your weapons and skills
which you learn as the story unfolds.

Why are the society researching the relics?
What happened to Mag's father?
Why was Linear sent to Mag?

All will be revealed ........